<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>謝秉潾的個人主頁</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #00d4ff;
            --bg-color: #0f172a;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --text-color: #f8fafc;
            --accent-color: #38bdf8;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft JhengHei', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #0072ff);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
        }

        h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 1.8rem; }
        
        .university {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .department {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .info-list {
            text-align: left;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .info-label { color: #94a3b8; }

        /* 興趣區塊樣式 */
        .interest-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .interest-item {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .interest-item:hover {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--bg-color);
        }

        .btn-contact {
            display: block;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff, #0072ff);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-contact:hover {
            filter: brightness(1.1);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="profile-img">謝</div>
    <div class="university">國立金門大學</div>
    <div class="department">資訊工程學系</div>
    <h1>謝秉潾</h1>
    
    <div class="section-title">基本資料</div>
    <div class="info-list">
        <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">學號</span>
            <span class="info-value">111410542</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">信箱</span>
            <span class="info-value">lingyue9688@gmail.com</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">個人興趣</div>
    <div class="interest-tags">
        <div class="interest-item">🎮 挑戰各類電玩</div>
        <div class="interest-item">🏓 喜愛打桌球</div>
        <div class="interest-item">🚀 探索科技議題</div>
    </div>

    <a href="mailto:lingyue9688@gmail.com" class="btn-contact">聯繫我</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
